<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-359] The configuration file for LNet router is wrong on 15.5</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-359</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following sentence :&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;Lustre_routes_config sets or cleans up LNET routes from the specified config file. /etc/sysconfig/lustre_routes.conf file can be used to automatically configure routes on LNET startup.&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
should be:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;Lustre_routes_config sets or cleans up LNET routes from the specified config file /etc/sysconfig/lnet_routes.conf file can be used to automatically configure routes on LNET startup.&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is based on the code into &lt;tt&gt;/etc/init.d/lnet&lt;/tt&gt; script.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
